  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to libkexiv2</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libkexiv2</application> package contains a wrapper
      around Exiv2 library to manipulate pictures metadata as EXIF/IPTC
      and XMP. 
    </para>

    &lfs76_checked;

